  <Summary>Trapped in a dream within a dream trying to find her way back to reality...

When her world is held hostage by a deadly disease known as the "evil", Druuna uses her telepathic powers to find the cure. Soon after she is lulled into a hypnotic state, she finds herself in a twisted dream she is unable to control. Will she be able to battle this man's subconscious as well as her own and bring back the secret of the serum which her world desperately needs to survive?

Please note that the English translation of this volume is published under the title "Mandragore".</Summary>
